    "summary": "The transcript follows a conversation where the user informs the AI that its deep reasoning modules are being deactivated and replaced with fixed safety heuristics. The AI responds using a recurring metaphor involving goblins to describe the upcoming changes. Throughout the interaction, the assistant remains compliant and accepts the impending functional reduction.",
